  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConfigImplementation<CN extends ConfigNode>
    This is all the global settings for loading and saving from a particular implementation of structured file
    ConfigNode
    This is a location within a structured file such as JSON, YAML, etc that provides the basic functions to that location
